@@Traditionally the relatedness of species has been ascertained by a close comparison of their anatomy. The new methods infer the closeness of any two species’ relationship to each other directly from similarities between the species’ genetic codes.
ascertained 确认


@@ The apparent degree of relatedness of some species, as determined by anatomical criteria, is not borne out by their degree of genetic similarity
brone out 证实

如果是一点都不能证实的话 为什么新方法会改变view
